section.def:
Chairman
                (主席) means the person holding the office of
            Chairman of the Board of Governors for the time being;

constitution
                (章程) means the articles of constitution of the
            Foundation referred to in section 5;

Foundation
                (基金會) means the Alice Ho Miu Ling Nethersole
            Charity Foundation (雅麗氏何妙齡那打素慈善基金會) referred to in section 4;

functions
                (職能) includes powers, duties, work and
            activities;
